data.description: Custom Southern Living Ranch home on 1.2 acres. This Dallas one story cul-de-sac offers private backyard with screened porch overlooking trees and creek below. Large master on main, with beautiful tiled bath. Split bedroom plan. Granite counter tops and LG appliances 3 years old. Basement features 2 full bedrooms and a den/family room. Large storage area in basement and a spacious two car garage with workshop area. Outbuilding for overflow storage.
